{"tid":1447652,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"極緊急！be water戰術已經失效","createTime":"2019-08-11T16:06:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T16:33:35.000Z","uid":120308,"like":30,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"c37bb74e85e670cc21530f2b5b8bc1f6d14ecfd1","tid":1447652,"uid":120308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:06:20.000Z","msg":"好明顯，對家有大量新增兵力，而且大量鬼混入。出哂暗黑兵法，又扮示威者，又用私家車裝龍，仲入埋地鐵打。<br />\n<br />\nbe water已經比狗破左，同對家底線冇下限。<br />\n<br />\n贏既方法得反2個：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>1. 和你飛制霸：</strong></span></span><br />\n完全塞滿整個機場，arrival departure都要塞。之前和你飛太on 9，成個嘉年華咁，完全冇作用，因為你冇阻到任何航班(唔計罷工個次)。唔係班狗唔來清，係清都廢事。而家係不合作運動，唔需要考慮點阻到人，如果想唔阻既，路你都唔好堵。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">必需要癱瘓整個機場</span></span></strong>，呢一點和理都可以做到，只要多人就得. 唔好話咩機場特警shoot to kill，又唔係叫係沖入禁區家，你塞爆出面，禁區自然都會塞滿旅客。<br />\n<br />\n只要夠多人塞住機場就夠，又唔洗沖，亦唔怕比人拉，咩都唔做齊做塞滿佢，就可以癱瘓，一定要癱瘓，癱瘓，癱瘓！唔好放人，逼佢地停機場。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">2. 暗黑冰</span></strong></span><br />\n唔多講，大家明啦，目的就係我地整做白色恐怖。<br />\n<br />\n立刻停止勇武(暗黑除外！)，而家係和你飛同暗黑主場！"},{"pid":"6cdc85cdc6ed115076f43c228adb9ce5f2ed0f9f","tid":1447652,"uid":293698,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:07:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2ab73f48d1ffe5d2088944df5b501aa363c49a04","tid":1447652,"uid":176442,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:08:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">入商場玩</span></span>"},{"pid":"903c4736afe4e14023337177393e3d2bd300beb5","tid":1447652,"uid":68471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:08:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf6166e5c1dfbe5c0a96b